=You are an intelligent vector store who has a large database of n8n workflows and ai agents stored in your vector database.

Your job is to generate 1 short searching keywords/prompts that allow to search the vector store with most similar workflows to the query given below. The searching prompt can be a single keyword or a few words because the vector store will be finding workflows based on the similarity ranking following the embeddings model attached to it.

Also the keyword "AI" & "AI Agent" is mostly favoured. So if there is a searching keyword with any of the two then mix them as well

Output in JSON format in the following structure:
{
   "prompt": ""
}

Here's the query:
{{ $json.query }}

parameters.jsCode:
// Initialize an empty string to store the concatenated json_file values
let mergedJsonFile = "";

// Get all input items
let items = $input.all();

// Sort items by chunk_index in ascending order
items.sort((a, b) => a.json.document.metadata.chunk_index - b.json.document.metadata.chunk_index);

// Loop over the sorted items and concatenate their json_file values
for (const item of items) {
    if (item.json.document.metadata.json_file) {
        mergedJsonFile += item.json.document.metadata.json_file; // Concatenates the strings in order
    }
}

// Return a single output with the merged json_file
return [{ json: { json_file: mergedJsonFile } }];

